code:
graph TD
    subgraph "Tree Detection"
        PLR[Logistics_Warehouse] --> SCAN[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
        SCAN --> LOGS[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
        LOGS --> CLUSTER[Logistics_FleetManagement]
        CLUSTER --> BASE[Logistics_FleetManagement]
        BASE --> CHECK{Logistics_DeliveryRoute}
        CHECK -->|No| ADD[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
        CHECK -->|Yes| SKIP[Logistics_StockLevel]
        ADD --> TREES[Logistics_Warehouse]
    end
    
    subgraph "Tree Cutting Process"
        REQ[Logistics_Warehouse] --> LLM[Logistics_StockLevel]
        LLM --> COORD[Logistics_StockLevel]
        COORD --> MOVE[Logistics_TrackingNumber]
        MOVE --> START[Logistics_Warehouse]
        
        START --> HEIGHT[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
        HEIGHT --> FINDLOGS[Logistics_TrackingNumber]
        FINDLOGS --> HASLOG{Logistics_TrackingNumber}
        
        HASLOG -->|Yes| CUT[Logistics_StockLevel]
        HASLOG -->|No| NEXTH[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
        
        CUT --> EFFECTS[Logistics_Warehouse]
        EFFECTS --> WOOD[Logistics_Warehouse]
        WOOD --> MORE{Logistics_TrackingNumber}
        
        MORE -->|Yes| HEIGHT
        MORE -->|No| NEXTH
        
        NEXTH --> MAXH{Logistics_FleetManagement}
        MAXH -->|No| HEIGHT
        MAXH -->|Yes| DONE[Logistics_StockLevel]
        
        DONE --> MARK[Logistics_FleetManagement]
        MARK --> COMPLETE[Logistics_Warehouse]
    end
    
    subgraph "Cut Tree Registry"
        MARK --> REGISTRY[Logistics_StockLevel]
        REGISTRY --> KEY[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
        KEY --> PERSIST[Logistics_StockLevel]
        PERSIST --> PREVENT[Logistics_FleetManagement]
    end
    
    style SCAN fill:#e8f5e8
    style CUT fill:#ffebee
    style EFFECTS fill:#fff3e0
    style REGISTRY fill:#f3e5f5
repo_description: Intelligent Agentic NPCs for Minecraft with LLM Integration
